<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-1961] Page with annotations renders fine with 1.8 but not with 2.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-1961</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Page 2 of the attached PDF (from a ghostscript installation) renders fine with 1.8 but not with 2.0. The other pages are not rendered properly with any version.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12698943">PDFBOX-1961</key>
            <summary>Page with annotations renders fine with 1.8 but not with 2.0</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
